 Conditions of Employment 
 US Citizenship or National (Residents of American Samoa and Swains Island) 
 Meet all eligibility requirements within 30 days of the closing date. 
 Register with Selective Service if you are a male born after 12/31/1959 
 Direct Deposit of salary check to financial organization required. 
 If selected, you must meet the following conditions: 
 
 Receive authorization from OPM on any job offer you receive, if you are or were (within the last 5 years) a  political  Schedule A, Schedule C or Non-Career SES employee in the Executive Branch. 
 Serve a one year probationary period, if required. 
 Undergo and pass a background investigation (Tier 2 investigation level). 
 Have your identity and work status eligibility verified if you are not a GSA employee. We will use the Department of Homeland Securityâ€™s e-Verify system for this. Any discrepancies must be resolved as a condition of continued employment. 
 
 Qualifications 
